Text:
Having problems unpacking the rar-files. Says that one part-file contains a CRC-error (in this case csi.615.hdtv-lol.r16). 

Got that problem with all the latest "TiAMO"-files, CSI Las Vegas + Miami included. At least one CRC-error per packed file. Previous files on the other hand worked fine. 

Any suggestions what the problem might be? 
Thanx in advance!
